Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:33.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在對我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說有的話也可以有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在追求我嗎
