Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:43.27,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,細川同學跑得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跑步真開心
